  "contents": "<article>\n  <header class=\"api-header\">\n    <h1 class=\"no-toc\" id=\"ngcontrolstatus\"><a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/forms/NgControlStatus#ngcontrolstatus\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a>NgControlStatus</h1>\n    <label class=\"api-type-label directive\">directive</label>\n    \n    \n    \n    <span class=\"version\"></span>\n  </header>\n\n  \n  <!-- INFO BAR -->\n<section class=\"info-bar\">\n\n<table class=\"is-full-width\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n  <th>npm Package</th>\n  <td><a href=\"https://www.npmjs.com/package/@angular/forms\">@angular/forms</a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n  <th>Module</th>\n  <td><code>import { <a href=\"api/forms/NgControlStatus\" class=\"code-anchor\">NgControlStatus</a> } from <a href=\"api/forms\">'@angular/forms'</a>;</code></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n  <th>Source</th>\n  <td><a href=\"https://github.com/angular/angular/tree/5.1.0-beta.0/packages/forms/src/directives/ng_control_status.ts#L38-L57\">forms/src/directives/ng_control_status.ts</a></td>\n</tr>\n\n</tbody>\n</table>\n\n  \n  \n  \n  <section class=\"directive-overview\">\n  <h2 id=\"overview\"><a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/forms/NgControlStatus#overview\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a>Overview</h2>\n<code-example language=\"ts\" hidecopy=\"true\">\n@<a href=\"api/core/Directive\" class=\"code-anchor\">Directive</a>({ selector: '[formControlName],[<a href=\"api/forms/NgControlStatus\" class=\"code-anchor\">ngModel</a>],[formControl]', host: ngControlStatusHost })\nclass <a href=\"api/forms/NgControlStatus\" class=\"code-anchor\">NgControlStatus</a> extends <a class=\"code-anchor\" href=\"\">AbstractControlStatus</a> {\n}\n</code-example>\n</section>\n\n  \n\n  \n\n<section class=\"selectors\">\n  <h2 id=\"selectors\"><a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/forms/NgControlStatus#selectors\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a>Selectors</h2>\n  <code-example hidecopy=\"true\" class=\"no-box api-heading selector\">\n  [formControlName]\n  [<a href=\"api/forms/NgControlStatus\" class=\"code-anchor\">ngModel</a>]\n  [formControl]\n  </code-example>\n</section>\n\n\n  \n  \n  \n\n\n\n<section class=\"description\">\n  <h2 id=\"description\"><a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/forms/NgControlStatus#description\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a>Description</h2>\n  <p>Directive automatically applied to Angular form controls that sets CSS classes\nbased on control status. The following classes are applied as the properties\nbecome true:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>ng-valid</li>\n<li>ng-invalid</li>\n<li>ng-pending</li>\n<li>ng-pristine</li>\n<li>ng-dirty</li>\n<li>ng-untouched</li>\n<li>ng-touched</li>\n</ul>\n\n</section>\n\n\n  \n  \n\n\n\n\n\n\n<section class=\"constructors\">\n  <h2 id=\"constructor\"><a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/forms/NgControlStatus#constructor\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a>Constructor</h2>\n  \n    <div class=\"constructor\">\n  <a id=\"constructor\"></a>\n  <code-example hidecopy=\"true\" class=\"no-box api-heading\">constructor(cd: <a href=\"api/forms/NgControl\" class=\"code-anchor\">NgControl</a>)</code-example></div>\n\n    \n    \n  \n</section>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n</section></article>\n<!-- links to this doc:\n - api/core/ChangeDetectorRef\n - api/core/Directive\n - api/forms\n - api/forms/CheckboxControlValueAccessor\n - api/forms/CheckboxRequiredValidator\n - api/forms/DefaultValueAccessor\n - api/forms/EmailValidator\n - api/forms/FormControlDirective\n - api/forms/FormControlName\n - api/forms/MaxLengthValidator\n - api/forms/MinLengthValidator\n - api/forms/NgForm\n - api/forms/NgModel\n - api/forms/NgModelGroup\n - api/forms/PatternValidator\n - api/forms/RadioControlValueAccessor\n - api/forms/RequiredValidator